{"tid":205630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新加坡樓價連續14季下滑 較2013年高位累計下挫11.7%","createTime":"2017-04-18T02:18:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T04:38:09.000Z","uid":13663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d5d481b9a1576523c723c921084ee14893dd264e","tid":205630,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T02:18:28.000Z","msg":"辣招奏效】新加坡樓價連續14季下滑 創史上最長跌浪 (10:31)<br />\n<br />\n文章日期：2017年4月3日<br />\n<br />\n這邊廂，香港即使推出樓市辣招，但仍無阻樓價強勁升勢，甚至有投資客扭盡六壬避開辣稅；但另一邊廂，新加坡辣招奏效，當地樓價今年首季再跌0.5%，創有紀錄最長跌浪。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡市區重建局（URA）數據顯示，當地私人樓價連續14個季度下跌，較2013年高位累計下挫11.7%，成交量亦較當年大減一半。<br />\n<br />\n不過，隨著美國加快加息，新加坡政府於上月亦宣布放寬樓市政策，將目前持貨4年內轉售物業須繳付印花稅的規定改為持貨3年內，各級稅率各自下調4個百分點，每級稅率分別為12%、8%和4%。原先貸款與估值比率（Loan-to-Valuation）60%以上，才能夠豁免總償債率（TDSR）的限制，即申請按揭貸款者每月攤還的房貸即使超過六成，亦可通過貸款申請，現在該豁免政策的門檻調低至50%。<br />\n<br />\n- See more at: <a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1491186852784&amp;issue=20170403#sthash.kMEaLjoj.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1491186852784%26issue%3D20170403%23sthash.kMEaLjoj.dpuf&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19tU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=32c83a5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1491186852784%26issue%3D20170403%23sthash.kMEaLjoj.dpuf&h=6bdfeb35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1491186852784&amp;issue=20170403#sthash.kMEaLjoj.dpuf</a>"},{"pid":"ed0f20a4af1e3786898a7602a1f51dca70f8ffdf","tid":205630,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T02:23:10.000Z","msg":"根本港共就係迫香港人離開香港<br />\n唔好幻想樓價會跌 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"782d00abed2c8650491ccc0c5a42eb7ce5f0d9e9","tid":205630,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T03:03:17.000Z","msg":"港柒:新加坡沒落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi